lead_paragraph: The International Olympic Committee says it has not received any request from Brazilian police for information concerning an investigation into a ticket-scalping scheme during the Summer Games in Rio de Janeiro.

headline.print_headline: IOC: No Request From Brazil Police on Olympic Ticket Probe
